Package: surveywts
Title: Tools for Survey Weighting and Calibration
Version: 0.1.0.9000
Authors@R:
    person("Jacob", "Dennen", , "jdenn0514@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre", "cph"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0003-3006-7364"))
Description: Provides tools for calibrating survey weights to known population
    totals using GREG, raking (iterative proportional fitting), and
    post-stratification. Supports nonresponse adjustment via the
    weighting-class method, effective sample size diagnostics, and full
    weighting history tracking for reproducible survey analysis workflows.
